00:11:29,145 --> 00:11:32,027
Jason sat really close to Mike, like three desks away.

214
00:11:32,127 --> 00:11:34,088
And later in production, I moved into the room

215
00:11:34,108 --> 00:11:34,988
with the coders on the team.

216
00:11:36,249 --> 00:11:37,170
One thing I forgot to mention is,

217
00:11:37,450 --> 00:11:39,211
in case you're not familiar with the term Strike Team,

