00:12:01,311 --> 00:12:05,495
So the first thing that we noticed, you know, we rolled onto the project and there were

226
00:12:05,675 --> 00:12:08,837
all these mockups and stuff, but we didn't really have any hardware.

227
00:12:09,758 --> 00:12:13,440
And I kind of looked out into the landscape of, you know, possible solutions for getting

